 <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.44</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σφᾶς αὺτούς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg002.perseus-grc1:37\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.37</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸν μὲν γενόμενον ὀλοφύρονται, ὅσα μιν δεῖ . . ἀναπλῆσαι κακά</foreign> for all the miseries which he must go through, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.4</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n73320.6\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pity,</tr_> <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">τινα</itype> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:245\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.245</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:364\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.364</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10:157\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.157</biblScope></bibl>.—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Verb, rare in Trag., sts. in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Prose, cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀλοφυρμός, ὀλόφυρσις.</for